Define Documentation

#define PM_PLAT_HEAP_ATTR

Define a processor-specific specifier for use in declaring the heap. If not defined, make it empty. See pmHeap in heap.c for its use, which is:
static PmHeap_t pmHeap PM_PLAT_HEAP_ATTR;
